<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="tr">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Hakkımızda | StarPhone</title>

<link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.10.5/font/bootstrap-icons.css">

<style>
:root{
    --dark:#0f172a;
    --dark-soft:#1e293b;
    --yellow:#facc15;
    --bg:#f8fafc;
}

body{
    background:var(--bg);
    font-family:'Inter',system-ui,-apple-system,sans-serif;
    color:#334155;
}

/* NAVBAR */
.navbar{
    background:rgba(15,23,42,.9)!important;
    backdrop-filter:blur(10px);
}

/* HERO */
.hero{
    background:radial-gradient(circle at top right,var(--dark-soft),var(--dark));
    color:#fff;
    padding:140px 0 120px; 
    position:relative;
    overflow:hidden;
}

/* Dalgalı ayırıcı */
.hero::after{
    content:"";
    position:absolute;
    bottom:-1px;
    left:0;
    width:100%;
    height:90px;
    background:var(--bg);
    clip-path:polygon(0 70%,100% 100%,100% 0,0 0);
    z-index:1;
}

/* Yıldızlar */
.hero-star{
    position:absolute;
    color:var(--yellow);
    opacity:.25;
    animation:twinkle 4s infinite ease-in-out;
}
@keyframes twinkle{
    0%,100%{opacity:.2;transform:scale(1)}
    50%{opacity:.6;transform:scale(1.3)}
}

/* Telefon silüeti */
.phone-silhouette{
    position:absolute;
    right:8%;
    top:18%;
    font-size:10rem;
    color:#fff;
    opacity:.08;
    transform:rotate(12deg);
}
@media(max-width:992px){
    .phone-silhouette{display:none}
}

.hero h1 span{
    color:var(--yellow);
    text-shadow:0 0 20px rgba(250,204,21,.4);
}

/* STATS WRAPPER - Ok ile işaretlediğin o alt boşluğa indirildi */
.stats-wrapper {
    margin-top: 100px; /* Değer artırılarak kutular daha da aşağı çekildi */
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
}

.stat{
    border-radius:22px;
    background:#fff;
    transition: .4s;
    border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.04);
}
.stat:hover{
    transform: translateY(-10px);
    box-shadow: 0 25px 50px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.12);
    border-color: rgba(250, 204, 21, 0.4);
}
.stat h2{font-weight:900;color:var(--dark)}

/* KART */
.card-hover{
    border-radius:26px;
    background:#fff;
    transition:.4s;
    border:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.04);
}
.card-hover:hover{
    transform:translateY(-10px);
    box-shadow:0 25px 50px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.12);
    border-color:rgba(250,204,21,.4);
}

/* ICON */
.icon-box{
    width:72px;
    height:72px;
    border-radius:22px;
    background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--yellow),#eab308);
    display:flex;
    align-items:center;
    justify-content:center;
    font-size:2rem;
    color:var(--dark);
    box-shadow:0 15px 30px rgba(250,204,21,.25);
}

.step{
    font-size:3.8rem;
    font-weight:900;
    color:var(--yellow);
    opacity:.3;
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<nav class="navbar navbar-dark sticky-top py-3 shadow-sm">
<div class="container">
<a class="navbar-brand fw-bold fs-3" href="/">
<i class="bi bi-stars text-warning me-2"></i>STARPHONE
</a>
<a href="/" class="btn btn-outline-light rounded-pill px-4">
<i class="bi bi-arrow-left"></i> Ana Sayfa
</a>
</div>
</nav>

<section class="hero text-center">
<i class="bi bi-star-fill hero-star" style="top:15%;left:12%"></i>
<i class="bi bi-star-fill hero-star" style="top:55%;left:6%;font-size:1.3rem"></i>
<i class="bi bi-star-fill hero-star" style="top:30%;right:22%;font-size:1.6rem"></i>
<i class="bi bi-star-fill hero-star" style="top:70%;right:15%"></i>

<i class="bi bi-phone phone-silhouette"></i>

<div class="container position-relative">
<h1 class="display-3 fw-bold mb-3">
StarPhone <span>Hakkında</span>
</h1>
<p class="lead opacity-75 mx-auto" style="max-width:650px">
Telefon ilanlarında güvenli, hızlı ve modern bir buluşma noktası.
</p>
</div>
</section>

<div class="container stats-wrapper">
<div class="row g-4 text-center mb-5">
<div class="col-md-3 col-6">
<div class="stat p-4 shadow-sm">
<h2 class="text-warning">10K+</h2>
<p class="small text-muted fw-bold mb-0 text-uppercase">AKTİF İLAN</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-md-3 col-6">
<div class="stat p-4 shadow-sm">
<h2 class="text-warning">50K+</h2>
<p class="small text-muted fw-bold mb-0 text-uppercase">ÜYE</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-md-3 col-6">
<div class="stat p-4 shadow-sm">
<h2 class="text-warning">%100</h2>
<p class="small text-muted fw-bold mb-0 text-uppercase">GÜVEN</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-md-3 col-6">
<div class="stat p-4 shadow-sm">
<h2 class="text-warning">24/7</h2>
<p class="small text-muted fw-bold mb-0 text-uppercase">DESTEK</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<div class="row text-center my-5 py-5 border-top border-bottom">
<div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
<div class="step">01</div>
<h5 class="fw-bold">İlanını Oluştur</h5>
<p class="text-muted small">Telefon bilgilerini ekle, yayına al.</p>
</div>
<div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
<div class="step">02</div>
<h5 class="fw-bold">Teklifleri İncele</h5>
<p class="text-muted small">Alıcılarla hızlıca iletişime geç.</p>
</div>
<div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
<div class="step">03</div>
<h5 class="fw-bold">Satışı Tamamla</h5>
<p class="text-muted small">Güvenli ve şeffaf ticaret.</p>
</div>
</div>

<div class="row g-4">
<div class="col-lg-4">
<div class="card-hover p-4 h-100">
<div class="icon-box mb-4"><i class="bi bi-lightning"></i></div>
<h4 class="fw-bold">Hızlı</h4>
<p class="text-muted">Sade arayüz sayesinde saniyeler içinde ilan ver.</p>
</div>
</div>

<div class="col-lg-4">
<div class="card-hover p-4 h-100">
<div class="icon-box mb-4"><i class="bi bi-shield-check"></i></div>
<h4 class="fw-bold">Güvenli</h4>
<p class="text-muted">Yetkilendirme sistemi ile ilanlar korunur.</p>
</div>
</div>

<div class="col-lg-4">
<div class="card-hover p-4 h-100">
<div class="icon-box mb-4"><i class="bi bi-gem"></i></div>
<h4 class="fw-bold">Modern</h4>
<p class="text-muted">iOS, Android ve Klasik için optimize edilmiş yapı.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<div class="row mt-5">
<div class="col-12">
<div class="bg-white p-5 rounded-5 shadow-sm border-start border-warning border-5">
<h3 class="fw-bold mb-3">Vizyonumuz</h3>
<p class="text-muted fs-5 mb-0">
StarPhone, kullanıcıların telefon ilanlarını güvenle yayınlayabildiği,
şeffaf ve modern bir dijital pazar yeri olmayı hedefler.
</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<footer class="bg-dark text-white text-center py-5 mt-5">
<i class="bi bi-stars text-warning fs-1 mb-3"></i>
<p class="opacity-50 mb-1">StarPhone — Telefonun Yıldızı</p>
<small class="opacity-50">© 2026 Tüm Hakları Saklıdır</small>
</footer>

<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>